Name: Do It With Hay
About the game: It’s a little funny game, in which you will be a worker on a small farm. You’re going to unload haystacks from truck to barn in time, since the driver won't wait long! The main thing - watch to your staminа and don’t overwork. Although, no one will prevent you from distracting yourself a little and diluting your work days with something funny. In this game you can do the following: Become the best among other players Drink Throw a pitchfork Listen to perky country Drink a lot Swim in a small lake Interact with extraterrestrial civilizations Don't get too drunk!
